type.description:
Specifies the particular type of document referenced.<br>

<b>Note:</b> 
<ul>
  <li>The type must include a LOINC or a proprietary coding but not both together.</li>
  <li>Multiple LOINC codings or a single proprietary coding can be provided.</li>
  <li>When providing a proprietary code system, use the following format where the code set is Millennium Code Set 72: <code>https://fhir.cerner.com/&lt;your EHR source id&gt;/codeSet/&lt;code set&gt;</code>.</li>
  <li>Example: <code>https://fhir.cerner.com/ec2458f2-1e24-41c8-b71b-0e701af7583d/codeSet/72</code>.</li>
</ul>

<b>Example:</b>

<pre><code>{
  "type": {
